              "text": "The wise men were experts in the movement of the stars and signs in the heavens. Their inquiry thrusts the provincial village into a cosmic concern. It is not the scientific data they are searching out, but a person to worship. True wisdom is not gathering information; it is adoration of God’s revealed truth.",
